<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="188300000t" end="213300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0">你不要太急於求勝</p>
<p begin="213300000t" end="223700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1">哈林斯大哥…</p>
<p begin="223800000t" end="271300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2">根據精靈們的說法</p>
<p begin="271300000t" end="295100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3">如果你現在就這樣會撐不住的</p>
<p begin="311700000t" end="321700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4">是…</p>
<p begin="339200000t" end="370500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5">進軍 進軍</p>
<p begin="480000000t" end="511700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6">警報響起 我的名字是"小蜘蛛"</p>
<p begin="511700000t" end="535900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7">(第二十一集 沒有我出場的份嗎？)</p>
<p begin="535900000t" end="541600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8">(第二十一集 沒有我出場的份嗎？)</p>
<p begin="541700000t" end="574200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9">即使受挫跌倒也阻止不了我</p>
<p begin="574200000t" end="589600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10">烏雲上吧</p>
<p begin="698800000t" end="723800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11">有時候偶然會假裝成命中注定</p>
<p begin="723800000t" end="751300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12">出現在善惡交會的立體透視街道</p>
<p begin="751300000t" end="780100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13">惡夢在迷宮裡不過是家常便飯</p>
<p begin="780100000t" end="807500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14">一般常識根本不管用</p>
<p begin="807500000t" end="858300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15">用老套的正面進攻</p>
<p begin="858300000t" end="904100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16">因為人生沒有你想得這麼簡單</p>
<p begin="904200000t" end="939200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17">驅使我前進</p>
<p begin="939200000t" end="992500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18">用這雙手創造勇敢的我</p>
<p begin="992500000t" end="1015800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19">「我最強 真是抱歉唷！」</p>
<p begin="1015800000t" end="1049100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20">狂暴貪婪的蜘蛛乘風跳躍</p>
<p begin="1049200000t" end="1071700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21">無法預測的新巨大波瀾</p>
<p begin="1098300000t" end="1127100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22">還沒結束</p>
<p begin="1127100000t" end="1156300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23">現在用最快的速度穿越黑暗</p>
<p begin="1156300000t" end="1188800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24">因為人生只有一次</p>
<p begin="1188800000t" end="1219200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25">只要直直向前跑</p>
<p begin="1219200000t" end="1284600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26">解開纏繞在心頭的線</p>
<p begin="1284600000t" end="1352500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27">就能跳到下一個興奮的舞台</p>
<p begin="1391300000t" end="1422600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28">初次見面你好 我叫田川邦彥</p>
<p begin="1422600000t" end="1441300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29">我叫櫛谷麻香</p>
<p begin="1441300000t" end="1470500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30">你們就是邦彥和麻香嗎</p>
<p begin="1470500000t" end="1522500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31">稍早和魔族大戰的時候</p>
<p begin="1522500000t" end="1543300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32">那應該是我們</p>
<p begin="1543300000t" end="1582900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33">真是的</p>
<p begin="1582900000t" end="1624600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34">有你們兩位強者當我的夥伴</p>
<p begin="1624600000t" end="1639600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35">是</p>
<p begin="1639600000t" end="1676300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36">他們好像是很有名的冒險者</p>
<p begin="1683300000t" end="1702100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37">羨慕嗎</p>
<p begin="1702100000t" end="1739600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38">是啊…因為我現在還沒有任何作為</p>
<p begin="1739600000t" end="1755000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39">很快就會有了</p>
<p begin="1755000000t" end="1797100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40">現在要去勘查結界吧 我們走吧</p>
<p begin="1797100000t" end="1820900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41">麻煩你帶路</p>
<p begin="1842100000t" end="1867100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42">好歹回答一下啊</p>
<p begin="1958800000t" end="1978800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43">這就是結界…</p>
<p begin="1978800000t" end="1999200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44">地下是什麼樣的情況呢</p>
<p begin="1999200000t" end="2040000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45">地下和空中都一樣有結界圍著</p>
<p begin="2040000000t" end="2097500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46">這樣啊 我想確認一下有多堅固</p>
<p begin="2097500000t" end="2109200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47">隨便你</p>
<p begin="2109200000t" end="2146300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48">好 大家離遠點</p>
<p begin="2270000000t" end="2299200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49">這把劍…是魔劍嗎</p>
<p begin="2315400000t" end="2366700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50">是用打倒的龍當材料做成的</p>
<p begin="2366700000t" end="2420000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51">我先澄清一下</p>
<p begin="2420000000t" end="2466700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52">不過還真厲害</p>
<p begin="2466700000t" end="2479200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53">菲覺得怎麼樣呢</p>
<p begin="2479200000t" end="2513000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54">如果剛剛那樣都不行</p>
<p begin="2513000000t" end="2542500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55">這就是精靈自豪的鐵壁結界啊</p>
<p begin="2542500000t" end="2564200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56">不知道夏目有沒有辦法破壞它</p>
<p begin="2564200000t" end="2594590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57">要是沒有破壞的必要呢</p>
<p begin="2594590000t" end="2627100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58">帝國軍隊的目的是壓制精靈們</p>
<p begin="2627100000t" end="2667100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59">如果結界很礙事</p>
<p begin="2667100000t" end="2682900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60">要怎麼解除</p>
<p begin="2682900000t" end="2748300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61">做法很簡單</p>
<p begin="2748300000t" end="2779100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62">或是讓在裡面的某人解除</p>
<p begin="2779200000t" end="2806300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63">妳的意思是我們內部可能有間諜</p>
<p begin="2806300000t" end="2828800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64">我只是說有這種可能</p>
<p begin="2828800000t" end="2887600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65">指揮帝國軍隊的由古會使用洗腦能力</p>
<p begin="2887600000t" end="2920000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66">我們是不可能向那種人屈服的</p>
<p begin="2920000000t" end="2980800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67">也對 但是為了以防萬一</p>
<p begin="2980800000t" end="3008700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68">不需要 不管他使出什麼手段</p>
<p begin="3008800000t" end="3047100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69">我們都不可能被區區一介人族的</p>
<p begin="3060400000t" end="3111200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70">應該小心別犯下這種蠢事的人</p>
<p begin="3111300000t" end="3130100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71">我們一族的恥辱…</p>
<p begin="3130100000t" end="3156700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72">怎麼還有臉回來這裡啊</p>
<p begin="3156700000t" end="3178000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73">什麼意思</p>
<p begin="3195400000t" end="3255400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74">不管怎麼樣 結界已經確認完畢</p>
<p begin="3255400000t" end="3285400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75">說得也是…走吧 安娜</p>
<p begin="3323300000t" end="3357100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76">我們非得保護這些傢伙不可嗎</p>
<p begin="3397900000t" end="3429200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77">這次距離住的地方太遠了</p>
<p begin="3429200000t" end="3464200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78">接下來該怎麼辦 要去找大家嗎</p>
<p begin="3464200000t" end="3478000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79">不 我…</p>
<p begin="3488800000t" end="3503000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80">老師</p>
<p begin="3503000000t" end="3539600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81">守衛到此為止就行了 後面由我來</p>
<p begin="3539600000t" end="3548400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82">可是…</p>
<p begin="3548400000t" end="3565000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83">不會有事的</p>
<p begin="3634200000t" end="3678000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84">在作戰之前</p>
<p begin="3678000000t" end="3691200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85">我們先走了</p>
<p begin="3701300000t" end="3740100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86">不用 其實我更想說給你們兩人聽</p>
<p begin="3740100000t" end="3758800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87">什麼</p>
<p begin="3758800000t" end="3782600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88">你們或許已經注意到了</p>
<p begin="3797500000t" end="3844600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89">我們是帶著別的世界的記憶</p>
<p begin="3855800000t" end="3878300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90">轉生者…</p>
<p begin="3878300000t" end="3892100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91">轉生者從出生開始</p>
<p begin="3892100000t" end="3927900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92">就擁有強大的技能</p>
<p begin="3927900000t" end="3982100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93">在這些條件的驅使之下</p>
<p begin="3982100000t" end="4032100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94">但是在我們原本的世界裡</p>
<p begin="4032100000t" end="4060000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95">也沒有魔物和魔族</p>
<p begin="4060000000t" end="4104200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96">雖然算不上和平</p>
<p begin="4116700000t" end="4165900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97">一時之間確實很難相信</p>
<p begin="4165900000t" end="4185400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98">我可以理解</p>
<p begin="4185400000t" end="4227100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99">可是就算這是真的好了</p>
<p begin="4227100000t" end="4297100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100">我認為是有人刻意操作的</p>
<p begin="4297100000t" end="4358400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101">神最終會盯上從異世界被召喚來的</p>
<p begin="4374200000t" end="4411700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102">精靈把這個神稱作管理員 與其抗衡</p>
<p begin="4411700000t" end="4439600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103">精靈之所以會協助保護轉生者</p>
<p begin="4439600000t" end="4465900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104">是為了防止強大的轉生者</p>
<p begin="4465900000t" end="4498700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105">並且奪走擁有的力量</p>
<p begin="4498800000t" end="4528400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106">神…管理員</p>
<p begin="4528400000t" end="4570400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107">感覺話題一下子跳好遠啊</p>
<p begin="4570400000t" end="4600400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108">我也不認為這些話都是真的</p>
<p begin="4600400000t" end="4646200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109">可是有自稱管理員的人存在這件事</p>
<p begin="4665400000t" end="4682100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110">然後管理員</p>
<p begin="4682100000t" end="4736300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111">要由古殺掉亞納雷德國王</p>
<p begin="4736300000t" end="4746700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112">什麼</p>
<p begin="4746700000t" end="4797500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113">等一下 妳的意思是這次的事情</p>
<p begin="4797500000t" end="4813800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114">夏目同學…</p>
<p begin="4813800000t" end="4837100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115">由古只不過是被利用而已</p>
<p begin="4837100000t" end="4882100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116">證據就是他的身邊有蘇菲亞在</p>
<p begin="4882100000t" end="4925400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117">蘇菲亞‧蓋倫</p>
<p begin="4925400000t" end="4959200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118">是站在管理員那邊的</p>
<p begin="4985000000t" end="5052900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119">我真的不想看到學生們像這樣</p>
<p begin="5064200000t" end="5100500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120">請你們守護這些孩子們</p>
<p begin="5130800000t" end="5181590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121">拜託你們 請你們一定要活下去</p>
<p begin="5230800000t" end="5252900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122">來整理情報吧</p>
<p begin="5252900000t" end="5310400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123">首先守護精靈村落的結界</p>
<p begin="5310400000t" end="5334200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124">很難輕易破壞</p>
<p begin="5334200000t" end="5395500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125">如果想侵入村落的話</p>
<p begin="5395500000t" end="5437900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126">雖然守衛很森嚴 但也並非不可能</p>
<p begin="5437900000t" end="5507500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127">反過來說只要徹底守好轉移陣</p>
<p begin="5507500000t" end="5557500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128">也就是說我們要做的事</p>
<p begin="5557500000t" end="5580000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129">有什麼異議嗎</p>
<p begin="5580000000t" end="5611300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130">如果有精靈被洗腦的話該怎麼辦</p>
<p begin="5611300000t" end="5638000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131">那我們也束手無策</p>
<p begin="5638000000t" end="5652500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132">真的假的</p>
<p begin="5652500000t" end="5692900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133">我們又沒有時間對所有精靈進行鑑定</p>
<p begin="5692900000t" end="5725800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134">但是完全撒手不管好像也不太好吧</p>
<p begin="5725800000t" end="5761600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135">最糟的情況是</p>
<p begin="5761700000t" end="5796700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136">再加上被洗腦的精靈引發暴動</p>
<p begin="5796700000t" end="5837500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137">最後結界因此被破壞也是有可能的</p>
<p begin="5837500000t" end="5872900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138">那樣可就慘了</p>
<p begin="5872900000t" end="5907900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139">你們是不是忘了最糟糕的事情</p>
<p begin="5907900000t" end="5965400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140">有吧 比夏目那個笨蛋還要棘手的</p>
<p begin="5965400000t" end="6012500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141">真貞子…現在是叫蘇菲亞吧</p>
<p begin="6012500000t" end="6053300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142">她擁有能讓魔法失效的能力</p>
<p begin="6053300000t" end="6079100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143">那算什麼 太犯規了吧</p>
<p begin="6079200000t" end="6118800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144">對了 那個能力對結界也有效嗎</p>
<p begin="6118800000t" end="6132600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145">不知道</p>
<p begin="6132600000t" end="6157900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146">這可不是鬧著玩的</p>
<p begin="6157900000t" end="6207500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147">而且對方那邊的轉生者</p>
<p begin="6207500000t" end="6257100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle148">能確定的是</p>
<p begin="6257100000t" end="6335900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle149">而且根據老師提供的情報</p>
<p begin="6384200000t" end="6435500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150">草間和京也…</p>
<p begin="6435500000t" end="6449200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle151">老師說過</p>
<p begin="6449200000t" end="6488000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle152">根岸只不過是站在管理員那方的</p>
<p begin="6488000000t" end="6530400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle153">也就是說</p>
<p begin="6530400000t" end="6562500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle154">也有可能兩個人都是</p>
<p begin="6562500000t" end="6592900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle155">妳認為京也站在由古那邊嗎</p>
<p begin="6592900000t" end="6647500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle156">考慮到他在前世的個性</p>
<p begin="6647500000t" end="6661300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle157">可是…</p>
<p begin="6661300000t" end="6713000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle158">是啊 京也說不定也變了</p>
<p begin="6713000000t" end="6745800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle159">誰幫忙回想一下草間同學的事</p>
<p begin="6771700000t" end="6807500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle160">抱歉 草間 老實說我忘了他</p>
<p begin="6807500000t" end="6824200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle161">真是的</p>
<p begin="6824200000t" end="6885000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle162">如果是忍 感覺會不知道這些陰謀</p>
<p begin="6885000000t" end="6930400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle163">除了夏目和根岸之外</p>
<p begin="6940400000t" end="6964200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle164">我已經開始煩惱了</p>
<p begin="6964200000t" end="7000500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle165">即使如此我們也必須做這件事</p>
<p begin="7000500000t" end="7045800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle166">抱歉在你們聊得正起勁時打斷你們</p>
<p begin="7045800000t" end="7054600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle167">什麼</p>
<p begin="7054600000t" end="7095000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle168">這場戰爭說到底</p>
<p begin="7095000000t" end="7141300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle169">我們只是前來助陣</p>
<p begin="7141300000t" end="7162600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle170">可是要是輸了精靈們他們會…</p>
<p begin="7162600000t" end="7185400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle171">你不要搞錯優先順序</p>
<p begin="7185400000t" end="7211200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle172">我們當然會盡可能替他們助陣</p>
<p begin="7211300000t" end="7264600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle173">可是如果你們會因此死掉的話</p>
<p begin="7284200000t" end="7328000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle174">我不想再看到重要的人</p>
<p begin="7328000000t" end="7355400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle175">菲莉梅絲肯定也是同樣的想法</p>
<p begin="7378300000t" end="7395800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle176">我明白了</p>
<p begin="7417500000t" end="7469200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle177">但我沒辦法看著人們在我眼前受苦</p>
<p begin="7469200000t" end="7523000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle178">尤利烏斯不是也說過同樣的話嗎</p>
<p begin="7523000000t" end="7535800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle179">是</p>
<p begin="7535800000t" end="7593700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle180">很好 那我們就按照原先的提案</p>
<p begin="7593800000t" end="7647100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle181">反正精靈也不會幫我們</p>
<p begin="7647100000t" end="7691300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle182">明天就是決戰</p>
<p begin="7691300000t" end="7702600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle183">是</p>
<p begin="7800000000t" end="7840800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle184">區區一個人族</p>
<p begin="7851300000t" end="7870900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle185">還真想看看</p>
<p begin="7883800000t" end="7923800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle186">是破壞結界還是從轉移陣入侵</p>
<p begin="7923800000t" end="7955500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle187">不管怎麼樣今天就會採取行動</p>
<p begin="7983300000t" end="8010000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle188">你是什麼人 你從哪裡進來的</p>
<p begin="8015400000t" end="8037900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle189">等一下</p>
<p begin="8037900000t" end="8055400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle190">怎麼了</p>
<p begin="8055400000t" end="8070000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle191">給我老實一點</p>
<p begin="8070000000t" end="8102500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle192">好險啊 會死的 你想殺我嗎</p>
<p begin="8114200000t" end="8151700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle193">原來是想殺我啊 這樣啊…</p>
<p begin="8151700000t" end="8188400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle194">是俊和葉多 還有阿邦 好久不見</p>
<p begin="8188400000t" end="8209600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle195">還有其他人也是</p>
<p begin="8209600000t" end="8238800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle196">這個語氣…你該不會…</p>
<p begin="8238800000t" end="8251300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle197">是草間吧</p>
<p begin="8251300000t" end="8281700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle198">沒錯…你們過得好嗎</p>
<p begin="8281700000t" end="8337100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle199">草間 你知道我們的事情</p>
<p begin="8350800000t" end="8386600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle200">要說是敵人…應該也算吧</p>
<p begin="8386700000t" end="8412500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle201">好 活捉他</p>
<p begin="8412500000t" end="8452500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle202">這麼多人一起攻過來</p>
<p begin="8452500000t" end="8475400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle203">草間 這項技能…</p>
<p begin="8475400000t" end="8510400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle204">(草間忍 忍者)</p>
<p begin="8510400000t" end="8522100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle205">這個嘛</p>
<p begin="8543800000t" end="8556300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle206">好可怕</p>
<p begin="8593300000t" end="8621600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle207">喂 俊 你想殺了我嗎</p>
<p begin="8621700000t" end="8645500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle208">分身 幻術</p>
<p begin="8645500000t" end="8657500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle209">包圍他</p>
<p begin="8677100000t" end="8690400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle210">等一下 等一下</p>
<p begin="8690400000t" end="8725000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle211">大家一起上未免太狡猾了吧</p>
<p begin="8782500000t" end="8831700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle212">可惡 竟敢欺騙我是簡單的任務</p>
<p begin="8831700000t" end="8845500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle213">你休想逃走</p>
<p begin="8862900000t" end="8883300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle214">大家也快點逃走比較好喔</p>
<p begin="8920800000t" end="8938700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle215">(炸裂劍)</p>
<p begin="8938800000t" end="8960900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle216">大家現在馬上逃到外面去</p>
<p begin="8960900000t" end="8971200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle217">修…</p>
<p begin="8985800000t" end="9002900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle218">沒用的 放棄吧</p>
<p begin="9002900000t" end="9015000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle219">怎麼可以</p>
<p begin="9166300000t" end="9188800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle220">轉移陣…</p>
<p begin="9188800000t" end="9228800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle221">讓魔劍的魔力引爆變成炸彈啊</p>
<p begin="9228800000t" end="9280900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle222">草間那個傢伙</p>
<p begin="9341300000t" end="9389200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle223">大家趁現在好好保存體力</p>
<p begin="9389200000t" end="9395900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle224">不對…</p>
<p begin="9395900000t" end="9410000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle225">什麼</p>
<p begin="9410000000t" end="9450800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle226">他破壞轉移陣的目的</p>
<p begin="9532500000t" end="9551300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle227">這是怎麼回事</p>
<p begin="9651300000t" end="9671700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle228">大家準備迎擊…</p>
<p begin="9686300000t" end="9702100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle229">結界…</p>
<p begin="9730400000t" end="9765800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle230">結界消失了 轉移陣也無法使用</p>
<p begin="9765800000t" end="9811600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle231">那些傢伙已經無路可逃</p>
<p begin="9959600000t" end="9984600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle232">這裡是我們精靈的院子</p>
<p begin="9984600000t" end="10005900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle233">我們就讓他們見識一下</p>
<p begin="10005900000t" end="10039600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle234">在森林裡向精靈們挑戰</p>
<p begin="10060800000t" end="10092500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle235">反抗神的精靈都得去死</p>
<p begin="10100400000t" end="10115000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle236">迎擊</p>
<p begin="10179600000t" end="10217500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle237">請妳再忍耐一下 悠莉</p>
<p begin="10217500000t" end="10235000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle238">技能…學生名冊</p>
<p begin="10235000000t" end="10242500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle239">(學生名冊)</p>
<p begin="10246700000t" end="10275890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle240">(夏目健吾 在精靈森林裡戰死)</p>
<p begin="10314600000t" end="10338390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle241">為什麼會變成這樣</p>
<p begin="10338390000t" end="10396600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle242">我只不過是想拯救學生們而已</p>
<p begin="10428800000t" end="10512100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle243">小岡 我好高興</p>
<p begin="10512100000t" end="10540400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle244">我也很高興喔</p>
<p begin="10605400000t" end="10617100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle245">根岸同學</p>
<p begin="10617100000t" end="10646700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle246">我不是說過別用那個名字叫我嗎</p>
<p begin="10646700000t" end="10683000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle247">蘇菲亞 妳不要插手</p>
<p begin="10683000000t" end="10718700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle248">是嗎 那我就在旁邊觀戰吧</p>
<p begin="10725400000t" end="10780800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle249">快點進攻啊 要是妳遲遲不來</p>
<p begin="10787900000t" end="10800400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle250">龍風</p>
<p begin="10846700000t" end="10870000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle251">那種魔法根本不管用</p>
<p begin="10937100000t" end="10977500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle252">將我的龍風抵銷的</p>
<p begin="10997900000t" end="11041200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle253">妳以為我還是那個</p>
<p begin="11041300000t" end="11073000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle254">明明是靠裝備的力量還敢說大話</p>
<p begin="11156300000t" end="11193000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle255">妳想知道嗎 我能變強的理由…</p>
<p begin="11242100000t" end="11261300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle256">你們別囂張</p>
<p begin="11280000000t" end="11293800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle257">快躲開</p>
<p begin="11313300000t" end="11352100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle258">精靈是異教徒 異教徒都得死</p>
<p begin="11395400000t" end="11420800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle259">其中一點妳應該知道吧</p>
<p begin="11420800000t" end="11476200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle260">技能魅惑</p>
<p begin="11506300000t" end="11565100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle261">我還有另外一項超強的技能</p>
<p begin="11565100000t" end="11590000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle262">貪婪…</p>
<p begin="11590000000t" end="11624200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle263">沒錯 七宗罪技能中的其中一項</p>
<p begin="11652900000t" end="11682500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle264">能奪走殺害對象技能的能力</p>
<p begin="11682500000t" end="11724200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle265">不過只能得到一點點技能和能力值</p>
<p begin="11724200000t" end="11743000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle266">就像這樣</p>
<p begin="11743000000t" end="11765800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle267">托妳的福我變得比之前更強</p>
<p begin="11765800000t" end="11790400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle268">謝謝妳 老師</p>
<p begin="11790400000t" end="11844600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle269">你究竟…奪走了多少人的性命呢</p>
<p begin="11844600000t" end="11866300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle270">犯下多少的罪過…</p>
<p begin="11971300000t" end="12007600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle271">老師 請妳稍微睡一下吧</p>
<p begin="12007600000t" end="12073300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle272">沒事的 老師那些中毒的思想</p>
<p begin="12132900000t" end="12171700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle273">竟然對學生做出這種事</p>
<p begin="12171700000t" end="12209600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle274">你…你沒資格說我</p>
<p begin="12209600000t" end="12231700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle275">妳做什麼…</p>
<p begin="12256700000t" end="12306300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle276">是結界</p>
<p begin="12317100000t" end="12337500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle277">但憑你是無法破解的</p>
<p begin="12350800000t" end="12367900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle278">呼吸…</p>
<p begin="12382900000t" end="12438300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle279">與村落的結界不同的一點</p>
<p begin="12479200000t" end="12528400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle280">結束了 夏目同學…不 由古</p>
<p begin="12604600000t" end="12616700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle281">真難看</p>
<p begin="12616700000t" end="12648800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle282">虧你還說過要我插手的大話</p>
<p begin="12660800000t" end="12682500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle283">別這麼說嘛</p>
<p begin="12682500000t" end="12748800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle284">我沒想到小岡</p>
<p begin="12759600000t" end="12786300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle285">根岸同學…</p>
<p begin="12786300000t" end="12820500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle286">不過這樣就結束了</p>
<p begin="12859200000t" end="12894600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle287">拜託誰來告訴我</p>
<p begin="12894600000t" end="12939600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle288">我有盡到身為老師的職責嗎</p>
<p begin="12980800000t" end="13006200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle289">抱歉我來晚了 老師</p>
<p begin="13031700000t" end="13051300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle290">修…</p>
<p begin="13312100000t" end="13346700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle291">煩死了！煩死了！我敢肯定是我贏！</p>
<p begin="13346700000t" end="13376700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle292">弱肉(吞噬)強食(殆盡！)</p>
<p begin="13376700000t" end="13411700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle293">"再來！再來！"真是無聊的遊戲</p>
<p begin="13411700000t" end="13443000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle294">可別給我小看人生啊？</p>
<p begin="13443000000t" end="13477900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle295">哎呀哎呀 上當了啊！</p>
<p begin="13477900000t" end="13511200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle296">上了低等生物的當是什麼感覺？</p>
